#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-new-polyline-decimation-strategies.md:1
msgid "Add new polyline decimation strategies"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-new-polyline-decimation-strategies.md:3
msgid ""
"The `vtkDecimatePolylineFilter` has been refactored to use a strategy "
"pattern. It used a default strategy based on eulerian distances. This change "
"brings 2 new available strategies :"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-new-polyline-decimation-strategies.md:6
msgid ""
"`vtkDecimatePolylineAngleStrategy` which uses the angle between 3 "
"consecutive points to perform the decimation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-new-polyline-decimation-strategies.md:7
msgid ""
"`vtkDecimatePolylineCustomFieldStrategy` which uses a specified `PointData` "
"array to gather the values used for the decimation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-new-polyline-decimation-strategies.md:9
msgid ""
"It is also possible to make custom strategies by inheriting  the "
"`vtkDecimatePolylineStrategy` class."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-new-polyline-decimation-strategies.md:11
msgid ""
"The new default strategy for the `vtkDecimatePolylineFilter` is the "
"`vtkDecimatePolylineDistanceStrategy` which implements the old eulerian "
"distance computation."
msgstr ""
